creator: May E. Southworth
description: LibriVox recording of The Great Small Cat and Others by May E. Southworth. Read in English by Mary Kay; Alice Armitt; Courtney Angermeier; Mike Pelton; Patti Cunningham; Julia Niedermaier; and Wendy Almeida. A collection of seven tales about cats. Caution: Some of these tales have very sad endings. (Summary by MaryAnn) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (85MB)
